  <h2>Welcome Visitors!</h2>
<p><a href="http://assets.codecloudapp.com/sites/5438407c6e6f64462d020000/b8cf8ea1edd4bbe6e89aa4d5389dd9bf/434290%20HSC%20InMall%20Brochure%20Spring%202015.pdf">Click here</a>, to download our tourism brochure which includes mall maps and a full store listing. Look for our <a href="http://assets.codecloudapp.com/sites/5438407c6e6f64462d020000/b8cf8ea1edd4bbe6e89aa4d5389dd9bf/11921HSC%20Where%20Ad%20SUMMER%202015%20HR.pdf" target="_blank">ad</a> in Where Magazine to receive a $5 Halifax Shopping Centre gift card to enjoy during your visit!</p>
<h5>Group Tours</h5>
<p>Halifax Shopping Centre welcomes motor coaches, convention delegates and all charter groups. A customized shopping expedition can be exclusively created for your group including special offers and transportation if needed. For more information e-mail us at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:hfxcustomerservice@20vic.com">hfxcustomerservice@20vic.com</a> or call 902-454-8666 ext. 225.</p>
<h5>Directions</h5>
<p>Located directly off Highway #102 and within minutes of downtown and Bayerâ€™s Lake Park. Halifax Shopping Centre is easily accessed from all directions.</p>
