<h5>Shop &amp; Stay</h5>
<p>Over a dozen hotels are within five kilometers of the centre with the closest being Best Western Chocolate Lake, Atlantica Hotel Halifax and Holiday Inn Express.</p>
<p>Enjoy a Shop &amp; Stay package, including&nbsp;a Halifax Shopping Centre Gift Card. Available at the following hotels:</p>

<p><a target="_blank" href="http://www.futureinns.com/index.php/packages">Future Inns Halifax</a></p>
